@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_illveb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = 0.39
    v0 = 0.88
    v1 = (tmp - wp.sin((v0 + 0.71 / v2 + 0.39)))
    tmp = (0.79 - (wp.abs(v2 + 0.21) + wp.cos(v2 + 0.46)))
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.exp(v0 + 0.79) + wp.abs(v1 + 0.71)))
    v2 = v2
    v0 = wp.cos((v0 / wp.cos(v1 + 0.27)))
    v0 = (v0 - v1)
    data[tid] = v0
